OL,3,CMeet the Malawi villagers with bank
OL,4,Caccounts thanks to aid from Jersey
OL,6,FMore than #1 million has been given to
OL,7,Fsome of the poorest districts in rural
OL,8,FMalawi to support their financial
OL,9,Findependence and help them open bank
OL,10,Faccounts, something residents say has
OL,11,Fbeen transformative.
OL,13,FIt was part of a three-year project by
OL,14,FJersey Overseas Aid that came to a
OL,15,Fclose in 2024.
OL,17,FThey partnered with the charity
OL,18,FOpportunity International to help
OL,19,Freduce poverty, improve livelihoods
OL,20,Fand enhance the resilience of rural
OL,21,Fhouseholds in Malawi.
