OL,3,CMeet the Malawi villagers with bank
OL,4,Caccounts thanks to aid from Jersey
OL,6,FLydia Baffour Awuah, Director of
OL,7,FInternational Programmes at
OL,8,FOpportunity International said:
OL,9,F"Access to finance is crucial, it's
OL,10,Fthe catalyst that will help people
OL,11,Fbecause most often the people that we
OL,12,Fwork with, they are creative people,
OL,13,Fyes, they are poor but they do have
OL,14,Fideas.
OL,16,F"What they are lacking is opportunity
OL,17,Fand that opportunity is access to
OL,18,Ffinance."
