OL,3,CMeet the Malawi villagers with bank
OL,4,Caccounts thanks to aid from Jersey
OL,6,FMalawi is considered one of the
OL,7,Fpoorest countries in the world - more
OL,8,Fthan half of its population is living
OL,9,Fin poverty and 67% of adults do not
OL,10,Fhave a bank account.
OL,12,FOpportunity International is helping
OL,13,Fto combat this: they have delivered
OL,14,Floan services to 6,326 rural people,
OL,15,Fwhile 24,000 have received training in
OL,16,Ffinancial literacy and business
OL,17,Fmanagement.
