OL,3,CMeet the Malawi villagers with bank
OL,4,Caccounts thanks to aid from Jersey
OL,6,FMeanwhile, 4,400 smallholder farmers
OL,7,Fhave benefitted from both training and
OL,8,Faccess to formal financial services to
OL,9,Fincrease productivity.
OL,11,F42-year-old Celine Harry is one of the
OL,12,Fbeneficiaries. She lives in the rural
OL,13,Foutskirts of Zomba with her five
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,FCeline said: "My mindset has changed
OL,17,Fin that I am now a financially
OL,18,Findependent woman who in the past
OL,19,Fcould hardly afford a packet of salt
OL,20,Fand had to beg from others.
