OL,3,CMeet the Malawi villagers with bank
OL,4,Caccounts thanks to aid from Jersey
OL,6,F"Now I am able to effectively manage
OL,7,Fmy own finances, I make my own budget
OL,8,Fthat enables me to buy salt as well as
OL,9,Ffood for my children.
OL,11,F"My life has changed and I am no
OL,12,Flonger the beggar I used to be."
OL,14,FMalawi's economy is heavily dependent
OL,15,Fon agriculture, around 80% of
OL,16,Flivelihoods are based on the sector.
OL,18,FMailosi Mikalasi is a Farmer Support
OL,19,FAgent who helps to educate people on
OL,20,Fvillage banking and how to turn a
OL,21,Fprofit from a smallholding.
