OL,3,CMeet the Malawi villagers with bank
OL,4,Caccounts thanks to aid from Jersey
OL,6,FHe said: "When they started to apply
OL,7,Fthe skills and knowledge about
OL,8,Fbudgeting, and when each of them
OL,9,Fearned some money, they started saving
OL,10,Fand used the money to buy goats, burnt
OL,11,Fbricks and built a house.
OL,13,F"I have evidence about this because I
OL,14,Fwas actually called to their home to
OL,15,Fsee for myself.
OL,17,F"So many families are being assisted
OL,18,Fand they are also transformed."
