OL,3,CMeet the Malawi villagers with bank
OL,4,Caccounts thanks to aid from Jersey
OL,6,FThe community in Malawi say they now
OL,7,Fhave hope for the future. Elen Gayesi,
OL,8,Fwho is another beneficiary of the
OL,9,Fcharity, said: "I managed to buy a
OL,10,Fpiece of land on which I built a house
OL,11,Fand I am no longer anxious about what
OL,12,Fhappens to me, as was previously the
OL,13,Fcase when my children were scavenging
OL,14,Fin the streets.
OL,16,F"My children are now well taken care
OL,17,Fof and we are happy."
